name: dns-stats
body:
### Welcome to dns-stats Home Page.

dns-stats is a covering entity for the implementation of the Hedgehog DNS statistics presenter and related developments. Read more about the Hedgehog software here: [About Hedgehog](https://github.com/dns-stats/hedgehog/wiki/About).

The full website for the [Hedgehog project is currently available here.](https://github.com/dns-stats/hedgehog/wiki) 

Expressions of interest for supporting dns-stats.org code like Hedgehog can be made on the dns-stats-users mailing list which will be available shortly. 

Watch this space for future updates on dns-stats.org and the open source release of Hedgehog (August 2014).
